Privacy Policy for Deemu
Effective Date: 22 May, 2025

Thank you for using Deemu. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information.

1. Information Collection
Deemu does not collect, store, or share any personal information. This app is a demo project created for portfolio and educational purposes only.

2. Data Usage
Since no personal data is collected, we do not use your information for analytics, marketing, or any third-party services.

3. Permissions
Deemu may request basic permissions (such as internet access) required to display content or load product data, but no sensitive data is accessed or stored.

4. Third-Party Services
Deemu does not integrate third-party analytics or advertising SDKs.

5. Security
As no data is collected or stored, your privacy is inherently protected. However, we ensure the app adheres to best practices in terms of user safety and platform compliance.

6. Changes to This Policy
This policy may be updated in the future to reflect changes in functionality or legal requirements. Users will be notified of significant changes via the Play Store update notes.

7. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to contact the developer at:
